<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your Driving Voucher</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .voucher {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .code {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0056b3;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hi <%= firstName %>
                <%= lastName %>,</h2>
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You’ve Earned a Driving Voucher!</h1>
            <p>Great news—because of excellent driving from your drivers, you’ve unlocked a special discount.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="voucher">
            <p><strong>Voucher Code:</strong></p>
            <p class="code">
                <%= voucherCode %>
            </p>

            <p><strong>Value:</strong> R <%= voucherValue.toFixed(2) %>
            </p>
            <p><strong>Expiry Date:</strong>
                <%= expiryDate %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2>How to Redeem</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Visit our <a href="<%= claimdUrl %>">Create Ad</a> page.</li>
            <li>Enter your voucher code in the “Voucher Code” field and click “Enter”</li>
            <li>Check your voucher details</li>
            <li>Click <strong>Claim now</strong> to complete via PayFast.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>Don’t miss out—voucher expires on <strong>
                <%= expiryDate %>
            </strong>.</p>
        <p>If you need help, reply to this email or contact <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>">
                <%= supportEmail %>
            </a>.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><b>EaseTruck</b></p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>